                      <p>Here you will get the different categories of shayri , peoples views <br class="br"> and 
                        thoughts.
                    </p>
                  </div>

                  <div class="buttons">
                      <a href="/blogs">Explore</a>
                      <a href="#footer">About Us</a>
                  </div>
            </div>

            <div class="right">
